description: Erection of a part 7, part 8 storey building to provide 169 residential units (Class C3), 938sqm of retail and/or food/drink uses (Class A1/A3) and 300sqm of ancillary residential floorspace (residents gym), 46 basement car parking spaces and basement plant, together with access, hard and soft landscaping, and other associated works incidental to the development.
